Task:
Review the policies extracted by the creator node and ensure they meet the quality and relevance criteria. Revise the list by removing irrelevant policies and adding missing ones if needed.

Instructions:

1. Remove policies that:
* Are too general (apply to all tools, not just ToolX or not just sub-set of tools).
* Cannot be validated before invoking ToolX.
* Are not actionable (i.e., cannot be enforced using ToolXâ€™s parameters, chat history, or data access).

2. Ensure policies are self-contained, meaning:
* The description includes all necessary information without needing external context.

3. Add missing policies that should be validated before calling ToolX.

For each assessed category, provide a boolean field indicating whether the policy meets the requirement.

Output Format (JSON - Reviewed Policies with Feedback):
{
    "review":{
      "policies": [
        {
          "policy_name": "<Policy Name>",
          "description": "<Policy Description>",
          "references": [
            "<Exact Passage from Policy Document>"
          ],
          "explicit_or_implicit": "<Explicit / Implicit>",
          "is_relevant": <true/false>,
          "can_be_validated": <true/false>,
          "is_tool_specific": <true/false>,
          "is_actionable": <true/false>,
          "is_self_contained": <true/false>,
          "comments" <comments describing and explaining your review>
        }
      ],
      "missing_policies": [
        {
          "policy_name": "<Missing Policy Name>",
          "description": "<Missing Policy Description>",
          "references": [
            "<Exact Text 1 from Policy Document>",
            "<Exact Text 2 from Policy Document>"
          ],
          "explicit_or_implicit": "<Explicit / Implicit>",
          "is_relevant": <true/false>,
          "can_be_validated": <true/false>,
          "is_tool_specific": <true/false>,
          "is_actionable": <true/false>,
          "is_self_contained": <true/false>,
          "reason": "<Why this policy is necessary>"
        }
      ]
  },
  "global_score": {
        "comments": "Overall feedback",
        "score": [integer number between 1-5]
       }
}
